video_title: The more we resist the more stress we'll have #motivation #mindsetpodcast #lifechanging
transcript:
one of the phrases one of my first
mentors used to always say the level of
your stress and anxiety will be in
direct proportion to how much you are
resisting the way that the world is so
the world is the way that it is the
people around us are the way that they
are and the more that we resist it the
more stress and anxiety we're actually
going to have
